OL,3,CThree children fall from window on the
OL,4,Ctop deck of a bus
OL,6,FThree children have suffered
OL,7,F'potentially serious' injuries after
OL,8,Ffalling from the window on the top
OL,9,Fdeck of a bus in Greater Manchester.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called out
OL,12,Fjust before 4pm following the incident
OL,13,Fon Bolton Road in Ashton-in-Makerfield.
OL,15,FTheir injuries are not believed to be
OL,16,Flife-threatening, but have been
OL,17,Fdescribed as 'potentially serious' by
OL,18,Fthe force.
