OL,6,FAn enquiry is now underway, however a
OL,7,Fsenior officer said it appeared at
OL,8,Fthis stage to be 'an unfortunate
OL,9,Faccident.'
OL,11,FInspector Simon Barrie, from Greater
OL,12,FManchester Police's Wigan District,
OL,13,Fsaid: "This is a serious incident that
OL,14,Fwill cause disruption, our priority is
OL,15,Fto make sure the children get the
OL,16,Ftreatment they need in hospital.
OL,17,FThankfully we don't believe their
OL,18,Finjuries are life-threatening."
