OL,6,F"This does appear to be an unfortunate
OL,7,Faccident at this time but we will be
OL,8,Fmaking enquiries as to the
OL,9,Fcircumstances and liaising with
OL,10,Fpartners."
OL,12,F"The investigation is in its early
OL,13,Fstages and work is underway to
OL,14,Fdetermine the full circumstances of
OL,15,Fthis incident" GMP added in a
OL,16,Fstatement.
