OL,6,FBolton Road was blocked off and there
OL,7,Fwas congestion around the junction
OL,8,Fwith Golborne Road as emergency
OL,9,Fservices dealt with the aftermath of
OL,10,Fthe incident.
OL,12,FGMP said the road had now reopened
OL,13,Fafter officers had carried out initial
OL,14,Fenquiries.
