OL,3,CThree children fall from window on the
OL,4,Ctop deck of a bus
OL,6,FCouncillor Danny Fletcher from the
OL,7,FAshton-in-Makerfield South Ward said
OL,8,Fsome of the children had suffered
OL,9,Fpotentially life-changing injuries:
OL,10,F"As we know, three young people have
OL,11,Ffallen from a top floor side window of
OL,12,Fa school bus and have been taken to
OL,13,FManchester Children's Hospital, some
OL,14,Fwith potentially life changing
OL,15,Finjuries."
OL,17,F"I've contacted the schools involved
OL,18,Fto ensure they have council support if
OL,19,Fneeded. Sending my thoughts and all my
OL,20,Flove to the kids and families
OL,21,Finvolved."
