OL,6,FA TfGM spokesperson said: "At around
OL,7,F3.50pm this afternoon we received
OL,8,Freports of an incident involving a
OL,9,Fschool bus service on Bolton Road,
OL,10,FAshton-in-Makerfield."
OL,12,F"We understand that three children
OL,13,Fonboard have since been taken to
OL,14,Fhospital. Our thoughts are with those
OL,15,Finjured and we want to wish them a
OL,16,Fspeedy recovery."
OL,18,FThey added: "We are working closely
OL,19,Fwith the bus operator in supporting
OL,20,Fpolice with their enquiries into the
OL,21,Fincident."
